dataChecks.name: Budget Validation
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM validation WHERE format IS NOT NULL

dataChecks.name: Resource Allocation
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM data WHERE value BETWEEN min AND max

dataChecks.name: Timeline Consistency
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT id, COUNT(*) FROM records GROUP BY id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1

dataChecks.name: Performance Metrics
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM metrics WHERE timestamp > NOW() - INTERVAL 1 DAY

dataChecks.name: Milestone Tracking
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM milestones WHERE status IN ('delayed', 'at-risk')

dataChecks.name: Earned Value
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM earned_value WHERE period = CURRENT_PERIOD()

dataChecks.name: Issue Tracking
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM issues WHERE resolution_date IS NULL

dataChecks.name: Asset Management
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM assets WHERE maintenance_due < NOW()

dataChecks.name: Version Control
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM documents WHERE version = latest_version

dataChecks.name: Capacity Planning
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM capacity WHERE available < demand

dataChecks.name: Knowledge Base
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM knowledge WHERE last_updated < NOW() - INTERVAL 6 MONTH

dataChecks.name: Integration Testing
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM tests WHERE type = 'integration' AND status = 'failed'

dataChecks.name: Maintenance Schedule
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM maintenance WHERE next_due < NOW() + INTERVAL 7 DAY

dataChecks.name: License Management
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM licenses WHERE expiry_date < NOW() + INTERVAL 30 DAY

dataChecks.name: Reporting Dashboard
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM reports WHERE generated_date = CURRENT_DATE

dataChecks.name: Escalation Process
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM escalations WHERE resolution_time > SLA_threshold

dataChecks.name: Performance Benchmark
dataChecks.sqlSelect: SELECT * FROM benchmarks WHERE performance_index < baseline
